WEBVTT

00:05:28.845 --> 00:05:30.174
in Somalia,

00:05:31.269 --> 00:05:33.098
and here in Nigeria.

00:05:35.554 --> 00:05:36.896
For me,

00:05:38.057 --> 00:05:40.376
the stigma is personal.

00:05:42.122 --> 00:05:43.751
In 2009,

00:05:44.796 --> 00:05:47.902
I received a frantic call
in the middle of the night.

00:05:49.359 --> 00:05:51.707
My best friend in the world --

00:05:51.731 --> 00:05:56.870
a brilliant, philosophical,
charming, hip young man --

00:05:56.894 --> 00:05:59.045
was diagnosed with schizophrenia.